stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Issued

    Issued --> Active
    Active --> Suspended
    Suspended --> Active

    Active --> Revoked
    Active --> Retired

    Revoked --> [*]
    Retired --> [*]

    note right of Issued
        Identity created under a
        recognized governance authority
    end note

    note right of Active
        Identity valid and permitted
        to participate in governed operations
    end note

    note right of Suspended
        Identity temporarily restricted
        but not revoked
    end note

    note right of Revoked
        Identity permanently invalidated
    end note

    note right of Retired
        Identity lifecycle completed
        without revocation
    end note
